Task: FSRS Stability Normalization

Summary: Implemented stabilityToRetention sigmoid normalization function to convert FSRS stability (days) into 0-1 retention strength. Added comprehensive unit tests covering edge cases (NaN, Infinity, negative values, custom scaleFactor).

Files:
- lib/practice/srs-proficiency.ts (new)
- __tests__/lib/practice/srs-proficiency.test.ts (new)

Why: This is the foundation for the objective proficiency measurement pipeline, enabling card states to feed into existing computeObjectiveProficiency.
